you remember this moment.

00:55:19.280 --> 00:55:20.050
So I'm optimistic.

00:55:20.050 --> 00:55:21.460
I think that the world is
actually getting better.

00:55:21.460 --> 00:55:23.793
So the fact that you asked
this question means that it's

00:55:23.793 --> 00:55:25.435
right away you see the problem.

00:55:25.435 --> 00:55:26.920
You see the potential.

00:55:26.920 --> 00:55:28.590
Is it opportunity
instead of threat?

00:55:28.590 --> 00:55:30.780
And I think that's
a great first step.

00:55:30.780 --> 00:55:32.720
And the reality is
that every time I

00:55:32.720 --> 00:55:34.920
give this talk with
a different version,

00:55:34.920 --> 00:55:36.900
people face these
questions, which

00:55:36.900 --> 00:55:38.760
means that we all
see that, and we're

00:55:38.760 --> 00:55:41.600
both customers and
like companies.

00:55:41.600 --> 00:55:44.759
So if you do it to one
person in the evening,

00:55:44.759 --> 00:55:46.300
they're going to do
