00:55:51.540 --> 00:55:52.680
for good.

00:55:52.680 --> 00:55:54.690
We usually find
ways to exploit it.

00:55:54.690 --> 00:55:56.080
But I'm optimistic still.

00:55:56.080 --> 00:55:58.680
So that's my thought.

00:55:58.680 --> 00:55:59.735
To ask questions?

00:55:59.735 --> 00:56:00.340
Great.

00:56:00.340 --> 00:56:01.006
AUDIENCE: Hello.

00:56:01.006 --> 00:56:03.480
Thanks a lot for the
